lure of thunder on both Tukaraak + Hraashina.  I still have to be in melee range to hit, but when I am it always lands for full.  On most kunark epic mobs lure of thunder will land while others are iffy or impossible at best.<br>
<br>
On a mob with low hp, yeah manaburn would be nice and efficient.  But going into Luclin (and some of velious) it's completely worthless since it's long fights.  For instance the Imps in Ssra, although light blue at level 65, have an absolutely ungodly amount of hit points for like a level 50 mob.  Besides, any decent wizard should have SCS3 and Concussion and thus should be regular nuking from like 95% and going until oom without aggro if you're a smart wizard. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=quineloe>Quineloe</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 1798<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/2/03 5:06 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mana burn</span><hr size=1> well you need to work on debuffs then, I was able to do like 25k to her with lure of ro.. or are you not 65? <p>Sage Quineloe<br>
